Wednesday November 19, 2008.

Today, Alex&amp;#039;s guests include: author, retired professor of philosophy of religion and theology, and 9/11 researcher David Ray Griffin, and physicist, former BYU scientist, and founding member of Scholars for 9/11 truth, Steven E. Jones, and sportswriter Dave Zirin of Edge of Sports joins Alex with stories of his tailing by Homeland Security, and his knowledge of the Tillman affair.  Alex also discusses the important issues of the day and takes your calls.

Hour-1: News &amp; Open Lines then Marty of Cal Ben Pure Soap
Hour-2: News &amp; Open Lines then Dave Zirin
Hour-3: Dave Zirin then Ted &amp;#039;The Leprechaun&amp;#039; Anderson then Open Lines
Hour-4: David Ray Griffin and Steven E Jones
